title: Juno Beach/Juno Pier RV Lot for Rent
posting_body: ['Juno Ocean Walk RV Resort, $1,325 a month long term includes water, sewer, cable and use of club house.', 'Call for Seasonal pricing.', 'This is a LOT ONLY.', 'The picture is not the lot that is available.', 'Tenant pays electric.', "It can hold up to a 32' motor home, 5th wheel or tag along.", 'This Resort community is located across the street from magnificent Juno Beach Pier.', 'Walk to restaurants, bank, pharmacy, shops and Publix.', 'This large private development is a beautifully landscaped tropical resort that offers many amenities.', 'Resort Amenities include: Heated pool with spa, playground, variety of sport courts, tiki area, clubhouse, community organized activities and more!', 'Surrounded by year round sport fishing, world class golf courses and so much more including Roger Dean Stadium which is the spring training home of the Miami Marlins and St. Louis Cardinals, and the new spring training facility for the Houston Astros and the Washington Nationals!']
